
'''Esther Mujawayo''' (wavutse 1958) ni umusociologue [[Rwanda|w'umunyarwanda]] akaba na psychotherapiste . Yarokotse Jenocide yakorewe abatutsi muri 1994, ariko yayiburiyemo abantu benshi bo mu muryango we. <ref name="gibbons">https://books.google.com/books?id=2LZnBwAAQBAJ</ref> Ni umwanditsi w'ibitabo byinshi. Mu 1994, yashinze ''Ishyirahamwe ry'abapfakazi ba Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi mu [[Rwanda]]'' . <ref name="geneva">https://archive.is/20150424192913/http://www.genevasummit.org/speaker/14/esther_mujawayo</ref> Yabonye impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza muri psychologiya yakuye muri kaminuza ya University of East Anglia mu 1997. <ref>https://www.uea.ac.uk/about/-/region-s-successes-set-to-inspire-next-generation-at-uea-graduation</ref>

